# Changelog

## [0.6.4] - 2025-04-11

### Added

- Repeat guest tracking functionality
- Repeat guest indicator in entry display
- Updated guest form with repeat guest checkbox

## [0.6.3] - 2025-04-11

### Added

- Check-in/out date selection for entries
- Automatic stay duration calculation
- Date validation for check-in/out
- Duration display in entry list

## [0.6.2] - 2025-04-11

### Security

- Added file upload validation
- Implemented security headers with helmet
- Enhanced error handling
- Added file size limits
- Added MIME type verification

## [0.6.1] - 2025-04-11

### Security

- Enhanced input sanitization with:
  - XSS protection
  - Null byte removal
  - Unicode normalization
  - Control character filtering
  - Input size limits
  - String trimming

## [0.6.0] - 2025-04-11

### Added

- Comprehensive API documentation
- Developer setup guide
- Contributing guidelines
- Documentation section in README

## [0.5.4] - 2025-04-11

### Changed

- Updated Node.js base image to 20.19.0-alpine for improved stability

## [0.5.3] - 2025-04-11

### Security

- Updated to Node.js 20.11.1-alpine3.19-slim base image
- Added Trivy vulnerability scanner during build
- Implemented strict security patches and updates
- Added CVE-2023-46809 security revert
- Enhanced system security configurations
- Reduced container attack surface

## [0.5.2] - 2025-04-11

### Security

- Updated Node.js base image to 20.11-alpine3.19
- Added container security hardening with dumb-init
- Implemented strict npm security auditing
- Added automatic security upgrades for Alpine packages

## [0.5.1] - 2025-04-11

### Changed

- Optimized TypeScript build process in Dockerfile
- Improved Docker volume configurations for better data persistence
- Updated package.json scripts for TypeScript support
- Enhanced Docker container security settings
- Fixed uploads directory permissions
- Added container restart policies

## [0.5.0] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- TypeScript support with configuration
- Jest testing framework with initial tests
- Environment variables configuration
- Input sanitization using XSS
- Development workflow improvements

## [0.4.1] - 2025-04-10

### Changed

- Marked UI/UX improvements as complete in documentation
- Verified all UI/UX features working

## [0.4.0] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- Form validation with error messages
- Loading states and spinners
- Success messages
- Mobile-responsive design
- Dark mode support
- New CSS architecture

## [0.3.1] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- Upload directory persistence in Docker
- Automatic upload directory creation
- File permissions for uploads in Docker

## [0.3.0] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- Entry deletion with confirmation
- Photo upload support
- Date range filtering
- Search functionality
- Email notifications for new entries
- Enhanced UI for new features

## [0.2.3] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- Host authentication using JWT
- CSRF protection for forms
- Rate limiting for API endpoints
- Protected entry deletion endpoint
- Security middleware

## [0.2.2] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- MongoDB backup and restore functionality
- Backup script with scheduled backup support
- Backup/restore API endpoints
- Documentation for backup features

## [0.2.1] - 2025-04-10

### Security

- Updated Node.js base image to 20-alpine3.19
- Added non-root user execution
- Implemented Docker security hardening

## [0.2.0] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- MongoDB integration for data persistence
- Docker Compose configuration
- Database models and schemas
- Updated documentation for MongoDB setup

## [0.1.0] - 2025-04-10

### Added

- Initial project setup
- Basic Express.js server
- Docker configuration
- Guest book form (Name, Visiting From, Comments)
- Comments display page
- Basic README documentation

